# Kleilson Portfolio — Contexto

## Stack

- Monorepo: pnpm + Turborepo (ADR-0011)
- React 19 + Vite 8 + React Router 7 (`apps/web`)
- **TypeScript** strict — `.ts` / `.tsx`
- CSS design tokens (`apps/web/src/index.css`) — dark-first, Sora + IBM Plex Sans, accent teal ([ADR-0004](../../docs/adr/0004-visual-direction.md))
- Qualidade: `pnpm lint` · `pnpm typecheck` · `pnpm test` · `pnpm test:e2e`

## Estrutura

```
apps/web/content/     → JSON canônico (ADR-0007/0012)
apps/web/src/data/    → wrappers TS
apps/web/src/pages/   → rotas
apps/api/             → Fastify local
apps/worker-api/      → Workers Free (prod)
apps/decap-oauth/     → OAuth Decap
packages/shared/      → schema contato
docs/                 → ADRs, architecture, guides
```

